President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the reappointment of
Dr. Hajo Sani OON, Senior Special Assistant to the President on Administration According to a statement by Suleiman Haruna Director of Information to First Lady of
Nigeria, State HouseMalam Hadi Uba has also been reappointed as Special
Assistant to the President on Administration. Dr. Kamal Abdurrahman Muhammad,  was equally  reappointed as Special Assistant to the
President on Health and Personal Physician. Those  reappointed are
“all in the Office of the First Lady” the statement said.